title: DEN VITA MASSAJEN-(Die weisse Massai)2005.DVDrip.SWESUB
description:
Based upon an autobiographical novel by Swiss writer Corinne Hofmann, the film tells of a girl, Carola, whose vacation in Kenya takes an interesting turn when she becomes infatuated with a Masai. Carola decides to leave her boyfriend to stay with her lover. There, she has to adapt to the Masai&#039;s way of life and get used to their food which includes milk mixed with blood. She also has to face her husband&#039;s attitude towards women and what he expects from a wife. Nonetheless, Carola is welcomed warmly into the tribe she has chosen to join.
